author: cframpton
msg: Change the directory structure of what PLAYERGLOBAL_HOME points to so that -target-player works correctly again.   PLAYERGLOBAL_HOME should contain the subdirectory 11.1 which contains playerglobal.swc.  In other words, the path to playerglobal.swc should be ${PLAYERGLOBAL_HOME}/${playerglobal.version}/playerglobal.swc where playerglobal.version is currently defined in build.properties to be 11.1.
